data.description: Priced below recent appraisal amount.  Great property, unrestricted, 9.5 acres,  5 bedrooms 3 full baths.  Living/dining area, large kitchen with lots of cabinets and counter space, pantry.  Home is located on a  very private location but close to town, shopping and schools.  Small creek runs through property.  10x6 front deck and 8x16 side deck.  12x24 storage/workshop with lofts for storage on each end.  New gravel on entry drive, new A/C, inside and outside units June 2023.  Great place for kids and grandkids to enjoy exploring and watching the wildlife.
